husband last night.

1098
01:14:30,909 --> 01:14:32,076
He's coming over.

1099
01:14:32,176 --> 01:14:33,978
Ah, brilliant.
Fair play-That's great.

1100
01:14:34,078 --> 01:14:35,713
- I'm really happy for you.
- It's good. Yeah.

1101
01:14:35,813 --> 01:14:37,964
We'll try to
make it work.

1102
01:14:38,064 --> 01:14:39,285
It's for the best.

1103
01:14:39,385 --> 01:14:40,586
Yeah.

1104
01:14:40,686 --> 01:14:42,655
Come back and hang out,
have a cup of tea.

1105
01:14:42,755 --> 01:14:44,091
It's the last day.
We'll hang out.

1106
01:14:44,191 --> 01:14:46,702
Whatever, breakfast, whatever.

1107
01:14:46,802 --> 01:14:47,827
Listen to the tunes.

1108
01:14:47,927 --> 01:14:49,796
Or you can come over later,
whatever.

1109
01:14:49,897 --> 01:14:51,883
