01:15:15,575 --> 01:15:16,695
Would it?

1121
01:15:16,795 --> 01:15:18,897
- Hanky... Would it?
- Very interesting.

1122
01:15:18,997 --> 01:15:21,993
Be worthless though.

1123
01:15:25,305 --> 01:15:28,277
Come back later.

1124
01:15:30,310 --> 01:15:32,313
Mmm.

1125
01:15:36,117 --> 01:15:37,919
Okay, I'll come.

1126
01:15:38,019 --> 01:15:39,288
Yeah?

1127
01:15:39,388 --> 01:15:40,555
I'll come later, yeah.

1128
01:15:40,655 --> 01:15:42,024
Brilliant.

1129
01:15:42,124 --> 01:15:43,192
You sure?

1130
01:15:43,292 --> 01:15:44,560
Brilliant.

1131
01:15:44,660 --> 01:15:45,694
All right, then...

1132
01:15:45,794 --> 01:15:47,663
Cool. See you after.
Well done.

1133
01:15:47,764 --> 01:15:49,766
You, too.

