you know...

1139
01:17:20,911 --> 01:17:22,240
It's fucking brilliant.

1140
01:17:22,340 --> 01:17:23,508
Really?

1141
01:17:23,609 --> 01:17:25,561
Fantastic stuff.

1142
01:17:25,661 --> 01:17:28,565
That'll be a hit, no question.

1143
01:17:28,665 --> 01:17:31,129
When are you off?

1144
01:17:31,229 --> 01:17:33,119
What?

1145
01:17:33,219 --> 01:17:35,855
Well, I've a few hundred quid
for you

1146
01:17:35,955 --> 01:17:38,410
for a deposit on a place.

1147
01:17:38,510 --> 01:17:40,461
Going to come over
and see you

1148
01:17:40,561 --> 01:17:42,563
when you're settled in.

1149
01:17:43,798 --> 01:17:47,032
When do you think
you'll be able to go?

1150
01:17:47,836 --> 01:17:49,738
I'm going tomorrow, Dad.

1151
01:17:49,838 --> 01:17:51,790
Good man.

1152
01:17:51,890 --> 01:17:53,510
About time.

1153
01:17:53,610 --> 01:17:55,613
(chuckles)

