01:17:57,514 --> 01:17:59,466
Will you be all right?

1155
01:17:59,566 --> 01:18:01,518
What do you mean?

1156
01:18:03,455 --> 01:18:07,692
I was all right for years
before you came along, wasn't I?

1157
01:18:07,792 --> 01:18:10,061
I don't have to go now.
I can put this thing off

1158
01:18:10,161 --> 01:18:11,897
- for a few months.
- Go.

1159
01:18:11,998 --> 01:18:13,499
And the best

1160
01:18:13,599 --> 01:18:15,234
