01:20:15,173 --> 01:20:17,510
Yeah, I'll write her
a letter, yeah, yeah.

1204
01:20:17,610 --> 01:20:18,678
- (crying)
- You go?

1205
01:20:18,778 --> 01:20:20,046
- No.
- Yeah?

1206
01:20:20,146 --> 01:20:21,781
- Yeah. Okay.
- Okay.

